</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/SequentialArt" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/SequentialArt">Sequential Art</a></em>: The squirrel girls express their fear of open spaces by hugging a doorway in a <a class="urllink" href="http://www.collectedcurios.com/sequentialart.php?s=490">Stack.<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>
